    {
      "name": "RedemptionTicket",
      "docs": [
        "RedemptionTicket - On-chain proof of payment",
        "",
        "Merchants can discover their tickets via:",
        "",
        "1. PDA Derivation (if allotment is known):",
        "```",
        "let (ticket_pda, _) = Pubkey::find_program_address(",
        "&[b\"ticket\", merchant_pubkey.as_ref(), allotment_pubkey.as_ref()],",
        "&program_id",
        ");",
        "```",
        "",
        "2. getProgramAccounts (find all tickets for merchant):",
        "```",
        "connection.getProgramAccounts(programId, {",
        "filters: [",
        "{ dataSize: 8 + RedemptionTicket::SIZE },",
        "{ memcmp: { offset: 40, bytes: merchant_pubkey } }  // merchant field offset",
        "]",
        "});",
        "```",
        "",
        "3. Event Listening:",
        "Listen for `RedeemEvent` filtered by merchant address"
      ],
